  <title>Gio.PollableInputStream</title>
  <synopsis><code>
const Gio = imports.gi.Gio;

let pollable_input_stream = new Gio.PollableInputStream();
  </code></synopsis>
  <p><link xref="Gio.PollableInputStream"/> is implemented by #GInputStreams that
can be polled for readiness to read. This can be used when
interfacing with a non-GIO API that expects
UNIX-file-descriptor-style asynchronous I/O rather than GIO-style.</p>
  <p>Since 2.28</p>
  <synopsis>
    <title>Prerequisites</title>
    <p>PollableInputStream requires Gio.InputStream</p>
  </synopsis>
  <synopsis>
    <title>Known Implementations</title>
    <p>PollableInputStream is implemented by ConverterInputStream, MemoryInputStream and UnixInputStream</p>
  </synopsis>
